Toggle Night Light

The [prgm]night-light[/prgm] command manages gammastep, which adjusts screen color temperature on Wayland to reduce eye strain.

$ [prgm]night-light[/prgm]                       # Toggle night light on/off (default)
$ [prgm]night-light toggle[/prgm]                # Explicitly toggle on/off
$ [prgm]night-light status[/prgm]                # Show current status
$ [prgm]night-light set-temperature[/prgm] [arg-value]3500[/arg-value]  # Set temperature (1000-10000K)

[dim]Edit [cyan]~/.config/gammastep/config.ini[/cyan] to set persistent temperature and location settings.[/dim]
